      "description": "Offering an exceptional E46 M3, a true collector-grade specimen featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six. This vehicle maintains factory-spec compression across all six cylinders and exhibits zero VANOS rattle, with valve clearances recently adjusted to precise tolerances. The subframe has been proactively reinforced, addressing the chassis's primary structural vulnerability. Power is delivered through a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M differential that provides instantaneous lockup. The suspension remains taut with original geometry intact and no bushing deflection. This is a turn-key enthusiast example with a meticulous service log, presenting in a state of mechanical and aesthetic preservation rarely seen on the market.",
