      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in showroom-fresh condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since its original purchase. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster with zero rock chips, scratches, or swirl marks, further protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of any creases, and the original deep-pile floor mats look as though they have never seen a shoe. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It comes with a complete, folder-bound service history documenting every oil change and inspection performed by certified technicians. The engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, and there are absolutely no leaks or deferred maintenance items. Every feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the advanced infotainment system, functions exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. The sale includes both original master keys, the owner's manual in its original leather case, and the original window sticker. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a flawless vehicle.",
